Billie Lourd is showering Taylor Lautner with love on his special day. On Saturday, the Scream Queens star shared a birthday message to her rumored beau on Instagram, writing, "üíôüë®‚Äçüëßüíô happy birfday to my #numberonesie." Not only are they wearing matching onesies in the selfie, but Taylor is also giving Billie a sweet kiss on the head. Since the heartbreaking death of her mother, Carrie Fisher , and her grandmother, Debbie Reynolds , the actress has been leaning on Taylor and the rest of her friends and family for support.
